#~ msgid ""
#~ "**atime:** when set to \"on\", controls whether the access time for files is"
#~ " updated when they are read. When set to \"off\", this property avoids "
#~ "producing write traffic when reading files and can result in significant "
#~ "performance gains, though it might confuse mailers and some other utilities."
